    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动作类肉鸽游戏</h2>Risk the Dark 是一款实时动作肉鸽游戏，你将扮演一名努力逃离可怕黑暗的幸存者。<br>通过光明与黑暗的互动，各种重要的生存机制相互结合，创造出一种身临其境且具有挑战性的体验。<br>探索阴影，增强力量，寻找出口。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >孤立于黑暗之中</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/c8fe39ce040ae63a88cdf8acb8f872ba.avif?t=1769163680\" width=800 height=532 /></span><br>&quot;撕裂&quot;之后，怪物出现了。在战斗中，一颗被投掷的手榴弹将你困在了一个未知的洞穴中。<br>虽然活了下来但受到惊吓，你发现你并不孤单。<br>冒险进入黑暗以求生存。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >光明与黑暗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/0ec5e98e42cf0135d008584f933519e8.poster.avif?t=1769163680\" width=800 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/0ec5e98e42cf0135d008584f933519e8.webm?t=1769163680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/0ec5e98e42cf0135d008584f933519e8.mp4?t=1769163680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在令人窒息的黑暗中，创造光源作为你的眼睛。利用这些资源，照亮你的道路，驱散黑暗。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的战斗风格</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/a1aca6eb796f300078e39bb0bde460eb.poster.avif?t=1769163680\" width=800 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/a1aca6eb796f300078e39bb0bde460eb.webm?t=1769163680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/a1aca6eb796f300078e39bb0bde460eb.mp4?t=1769163680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>增强并完善你的构建，以充分利用你的旅程。<br>结合近战、远程攻击、投掷物和元素战斗选项，混搭出多样化的游戏风格。<br>使用装备、改装、消耗品和配件，以及技能精通系统来支持你的决策。<br>有了正确的技能组合，你将向他们证明，不需要英雄也能冒险进入黑暗。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特殊的首领战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/bb3d32e9decb6ba1aa945904801110f8.poster.avif?t=1769163680\" width=800 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/bb3d32e9decb6ba1aa945904801110f8.webm?t=1769163680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094800/extras/bb3d32e9decb6ba1aa945904801110f8.mp4?t=1769163680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在每个区域的尽头，你将面对一个特别可怕的敌人。<br>躲避他们的攻击并击中他们的弱点，将他们击败，证明你不是一个容易对付的目标。",
